Title: Sharknado 5: Global Swarming
Genre: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Fantasy, Horror, Sci-Fi, Thriller
Writer: Thunder Levin (based on characters created by), Scotty Mullen
Actors: Ian Ziering, Tara Reid, Cassandra Scerbo, Billy Barratt
Plot: With much of America lying in ruins, the rest of the world braces for a global sharknado; Fin and his family must travel around the world to stop them.
